A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Hate Crimes and Hate Bias – Definitions of Sexual Orientation and Hate Bias
3 Incident
4 FOR the purpose of altering the definition of “sexual orientation” applicable to certain hate
5 crime statutes; defining “hate bias incident” applicable to a certain requirement that
6 the Department of State Police collect, analyze, and report certain information
7 provided by certain law enforcement agencies; and generally relating to hate crimes
8 and hate bias incidents.
